  "text": "and units 1 → P (n, n) corresponding to identity morphisms of the objects n ∈ N in P . These operations satisfy relations coming from the axioms of symmetric monoidal categories. We refer the reader to Enriquez and Etingof [CITATION_1] for an explicit description of props in the context of modules over a ring. We denote by P the category of props.",
